t YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0px 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #8f959e;letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-author&quot;:&quot;dui!&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: #8f959e;letter-spacing: 0px;font-weight: 400;font-family: PingFang SC,system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Helvetica Neue,Hiragino Sans GB,Microsoft YaHei UI,Microsoft YaHei,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px 0px;border: 1px solid rgba(NaN, 10, NaN, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 12px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\">mureka.cn</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 16px;line-height: 2em;\"></p>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"margin:0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;width:100%;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span leaf=\"\">出来的效果还蛮惊喜的，一次抽卡，在情绪，节奏和氛围上，和我用Gemini分析出的画面描述匹配度非常高，</span></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">这段时间我印象深刻的还有吴爱花，一个纯AI的武打风MV，给我拉回去小时候在TVB看流星蝴蝶剑的感觉</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2em;\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我也想用Mureka V8把这个MV重新配成中文版听听看，会有什么不一样的。</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2em;\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在处理一些具有中国元素的音乐风格时，Mureka V8的理解力和表现力要比Suno V5更地道。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在生成三分钟的完整曲目时，V8能一直保持一个比较统一的结构和逻辑，人声的质感和器乐的分离度也做得相当不错。以后开车想听什么DJ版，自己做就好了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI音乐自成一个品类，当我的AI版Spotify！</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">比方说daft punk版千年等一回法海版，</span></span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 2em;\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span leaf=\"\">BTW，昆仑自己做的AI女团MV也很抓耳，</span></p>\n     <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">就在我以为这个工作流已经很顺畅的时候，我发现Mureka V8居然支持MCP，</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">有四种玩法，纯音乐，带人声的音乐，生成歌词，以及根据歌词创作音乐。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100020669\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0051355b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXmXibPvXWTFzOLE7aukZDSkycyj67N7drtq9X9DPtn8QUBk5mggKq30ZQAyOvy5OWYgIrHyoGXZ9Gg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">有MCP就意味着我可以把它做成一个Skill，一个可以被其他程序自由调用的模块，制作新Skills的思路很简单，只需要保证Claude Code里面已经有skills-creator这个技能，然后把MCP对应的github页面链接也丢给Claude，</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"background-color:rgb(103, 84, 140);border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:8px;padding:4px 14px;place-items:flex-start;display:flex;margin-top:16px;line-height:2em;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left !important;\">\n      <span style=\"align-items: center;justify-content: center;display: none;\"><span style=\"font-size: inherit;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">🌅</span></span></span>\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;\">\n       <p style=\"margin:8px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;width:100%;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">帮我把这个开源工具&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/SkyworkAI/Mureka-mcp\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/SkyworkAI/Mureka-mcp</a></span></span></span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">打包成一个Skill，只要我后续给出提示语，就可以帮我做出一首纯音乐。</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n      <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020668\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=825609a6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXmXibPvXWTFzOLE7aukZDSkyzKCaMkib3amRom6sKrcGmJZXvoc8icbwbQZIKNJGdnAvicWTaicibxNXib3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">一条完全自动化的配乐工作流就这么诞生了。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">我只需要把视频丢进去，NoteBookLM就会自动分析画面，根据知识库的提示语技巧生成音乐描述，调用Mureka V8创作音乐，最后再把音乐和视频合成为一个成品。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-br