各个元素做成了独立的模块，音乐家可以用跳线把这些模块以任意方式连接起来，创造出前所未有的声音。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:16px 0px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;min-height:20px;line-height:2em;\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">音乐创作，第一次变成了声音的工程设计。</span></span></p>\n     <div style=\"margin-bottom: 18px;display: flex;justify-content: space-between;flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <div key=\"89\" style=\"display: inline-block;flex: 1;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;line-height: 2em;margin: 0;minHeight: 20px;letterSpacing: auto;padding: 0 4px;\">\n       <div>\n        <div style=\"margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center !important;\">\n         <p style=\"display: block;margin: 0px;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 2em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.744\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"250\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 5px;box-sizing: border-box;margin: 0px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);padding: 0px;box-shadow: none;\" data-imgfileid=\"100020673\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=499a9888&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FYEhakvKZjXmXibPvXWTFzOLE7aukZDSky9rxNFUgkQDJsFqEm6iaIiaMib8jUrGED1y4H9eGLhibicrwBfLJtK9ZoVRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div key=\"91\" style=\"display: inline-block;flex: 1;color: #646a73;font-size: 16px;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingF